---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout 
  title="About Us"
  description="Learn about our automated content generation system and our mission to provide quality information."
>
  <div class="container-narrow">
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-6">About AdSense Automation</h1>
    
    <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none mb-12">
      <p>
        Welcome to AdSense Automation, a demonstration of automated content generation technology. 
        Our platform creates high-quality, SEO-optimized articles using advanced AI models, 
        then structures and publishes them automatically.
      </p>
      
      <h2>Our Mission</h2>
      <p>
        Our goal is to explore the potential of AI-powered content creation while maintaining 
        high standards of accuracy, relevance, and readability. We believe that automation 
        can complement human creativity, not replace it.
      </p>
      
      <h2>How It Works</h2>
      <ol>
        <li><strong>Keyword Research:</strong> We identify low-competition, high-volume keywords using automated tools.</li>
        <li><strong>Content Generation:</strong> AI models create articles based on comprehensive research and data.</li>
        <li><strong>Quality Review:</strong> Automated systems check for accuracy, readability, and SEO optimization.</li>
        <li><strong>Publication:</strong> Articles are automatically published and indexed for search engines.</li>
        <li><strong>Monitoring:</strong> Performance is tracked, and content is updated as needed.</li>
      </ol>
      
      <h2>Our Niches</h2>
      <p>
        We focus on three primary areas where we believe automated content can provide genuine value:
      </p>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Personal Finance:</strong> Practical advice on saving, investing, and managing money.</li>
        <li><strong>Home Improvement:</strong> DIY guides, repair tutorials, and renovation tips.</li>
        <li><strong>Health & Wellness:</strong> General wellness information, fitness tips, and healthy living advice.</li>
      </ul>
      
      <div class="bg-yellow-50 border-l-4 border-yellow-400 p-4 my-8">
        <div class="flex">
          <div class="flex-shrink-0">
            <span class="text-yellow-500 text-xl">⚠️</span>
          </div>
          <div class="ml-3">
            <p class="text-yellow-800">
              <strong>Important Disclaimer:</strong> This website is an experiment in automated content generation. 
              Articles are created by AI and should be verified with professional advice when appropriate. 
              For medical, financial, or legal matters, always consult qualified professionals.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <h2>Technology Stack</h2>
      <p>
        Our system is built on modern, scalable technologies:
      </p>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Frontend:</strong> Astro for blazing-fast static site generation</li>
        <li><strong>Styling:</strong> Tailwind CSS for responsive design</li>
        <li><strong>Database:</strong> Supabase (PostgreSQL) for content storage</li>
        <li><strong>Deployment:</strong> Vercel for automatic builds and hosting</li>
        <li><strong>Automation:</strong> GitHub Actions for CI/CD pipelines</li>
        <li><strong>AI Models:</strong> Various LLMs for content generation</li>
      </ul>
      
      <h2>Transparency</h2>
      <p>
        We believe in transparency about our automated processes. Each article includes a note about 
        its AI-assisted creation. We continuously monitor and improve our systems to ensure content quality.
      </p>
      
      <p>
        This project is open-source and available for educational purposes. We welcome feedback 
        and collaboration from the developer and SEO communities.
      </p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-xl p-8">
      <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Contact & Feedback</h3>
      <p class="mb-4">
        Have questions or feedback about our automated content system? We'd love to hear from you.
      </p>
      <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-primary">
        Contact Us
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>